{"tid":686660,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[考古] 兒童樂園大合集","createTime":"2018-06-01T13:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T09:54:12.000Z","uid":37125,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ecf696c8c89d3c203f9ad2f3ecbd21693d2d595","tid":686660,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/5ffe7f0fe91a878fbbf8b83638b42fa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F5ffe7f0fe91a878fbbf8b83638b42fa2.png&h=018e7e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《兒童樂園》是香港一份由1953至1995年間出版的兒童刊物，每半月出版一期，為香港定期出版的重要兒童刊物之一，亦是香港首份以全彩色印刷的兒童書刊。1994年12月16日發行最後一期（1006期）後，因經濟問題而宣佈在1995年停刊[1]。2013年11月8日，前社長張浚華與一位不具名《兒童樂園》讀者將一共1006期《兒童樂園》電子化，並設立網站免費供人下載[2] 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://childrenparadise.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchildrenparadise.net%2F&d=KZr3dx1hxODI1fEvkQuDHb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=951b1841\" target=\"_blank\">http://childrenparadise.net/</a>"},{"pid":"66ecddb418f04b416c1d539e03e3888ffe3e850f","tid":686660,"uid":70487,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"停刊個陣依度好多人未出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad56d8bab0658fe5f2db2613fe6d76bfdebe5052","tid":686660,"uid":37125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ecddb418f04b416c1d539e03e3888ffe3e850f","tid":686660,"uid":70487,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"停刊個陣依度好多人未出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:32:08.000Z","msg":"其實係咪無論去到幾多十年之後, 社會表面有幾進步都好, 都重係會有一大班人只見新與舊, 而不見劣與優?<br />\n我都係90年代先開始睇, 同期重有啲差唔多 size 嘅老翻超人書."},{"pid":"62a0e3443f1fe52d9f9ec04599bd382e5497f177","tid":686660,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"羅冠樵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm